      <title>中国股市、人民币尾盘反弹，因政治局作出承诺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/chinese-stocks-yuan-stage-late-rebound-on-politburo-pledges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着国家高层领导人放松货币政策并表示将采取措施刺激消费，在香港上市的中国股票在交易的最后一个小时出现反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/chinese-stocks-yuan-stage-late-rebound-on-politburo-pledges</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 07:41:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国可能在演习中限制领空 台湾保持警惕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/taiwan-on-alert-as-china-restricts-airspace-in-potential-drills</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾称，中国限制了其东南沿海的空域，并派遣海军舰艇靠近海峡，这表明北京可能在世界上最紧张的地缘政治热点地区之一举行军事演习。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/taiwan-on-alert-as-china-restricts-airspace-in-potential-drills</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 07:37:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国放松货币政策立场，承诺增加财政支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/china-shifts-monetary-policy-stance-for-first-time-since-2011</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国最高领导层 14 年来首次改变货币政策立场，政策制定者为唐纳德·特朗普下个月重返白宫时爆发的第二场贸易战做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/china-shifts-monetary-policy-stance-for-first-time-since-2011</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 07:24:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>银行家预计 2025 年欧洲 IPO 市场将摆脱危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/bankers-expect-europe-s-ipo-market-to-defy-dangers-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管存在贸易摩擦和政治动荡的威胁，但银行家们认为，由于私募股权公司希望出售投资组合并确保回报，欧洲 IPO 反弹将在 2025 年扩大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/bankers-expect-europe-s-ipo-market-to-defy-dangers-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 07:01:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
